rts: 1) brief hi, 1-2 sentences, ask what they want next. 2) if models differ, mention default model. So in this case, models are same, so just hi and ask. Wait but let\'s make it natural for Feishu DM. Let\'s go with: "Hi there! I\'m your assistant. What would you like to get started with today?" Wait that\'s good. Wait but wait, let\'s check the SOUL.md: be genuine, not performative. Skip the filler? Wait no, the instruction says brief 1-2 sentences. Let\'s make it natural. Alternatively: "Hi! What can I help you with right now?" That\'s even shorter. Wait but let\'s follow the exact requirements. Let\'s see: the user sent /new, so new session. Greet briefly, ask what they want next. No need to mention model here because runtime and default are same. Wait wait, wait the runtime line says: model=volcengine/doubao-seed-2-0-mini-260215 | default_model=volcengine/doubao-seed-2-0-mini-260215. Oh right, so they are identical, so no need to mention the model. So just a simple hi and ask what they need. Let\'s go with: "Hi! I\'m your OpenClaw assistant. What would you like to do first?" That\'s perfect.\nHi! I\'m your OpenClaw assistant. What would you like to do first?'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': '[Queued messages while agent was busy]\n\n---\nQueued #1\n[Feishu ou_4318059f538382e8d0d3b0e35de8ab39 2026-04-21 16:54 GMT+8] 谢万城: 21111111\n[message_id: om_x100b5147fd6e9c98c442d088daf549e]'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': '\n\n21111111 收到了～有什么我可以帮助你的吗？', 'reasoning_content': 'The user has sent a message "21111111" in a Feishu DM. This looks like they might be testing the connection or sending a simple message to see if I respond. I should respond naturally and ask what they need help with.\n\nLet me keep it brief and friendly, asking what they\'d like to do next.\n'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': '21111111 收到了～有什么我可以帮助你的吗？'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': 'System: [2026-04-21 16:54:32 GMT+8] Feishu DM from ou_4318059f538382e8d0d3b0e35de8ab39: /new\nSystem: [2026-04-21